{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/iphone-game-of-the-year-2017/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"iPhone Game Of the Year 2017","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apple Design Award atau yang biasa disebut dengan ADA adalah acara khusus tahunan yang diselenggarakan oleh Apple Inc. Acara Apple Design Award dimaksudkan untuk mengenali perangkat lunak dan perangkat-perangkat keras Macintosh dan iOS <em>software</em> dan <em>hardware</em> yang diproduksi oleh pengembang usaha independen, sekaligus penggunaan produk Apple yang terbaik dan paling kreatif. Apple Design Awards juga memperkenalkan aplikasi mutakhir yang mencerminkan desain, inovasi, dan teknologi terbaik di platform Apple.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ADA terdiri dari beberapa kategori yang bervariasi dari tahun ke tahun. Apple Design Award telah diadakan setiap tahun sejak tahun 1996. Di dua tahun pertama, mereka dikenal sebagai Human Interface Design Excellence (HIDE) Awards. Sejak tahun 2003, penghargaan ini dirancang dengan logo Apple yang bersinar saat disentuh. Penghargaan baru ini direkayasa dan dibangun oleh Sparkfactor Design.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_31736\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-31736\" data-attachment-id=\"31736\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iphone-game-of-the-year-2017/attachment/6-1-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1512747059&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : www.apple.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : www.apple.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-31736\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : www.apple.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-31736\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : www.apple.com)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pada ajang Apple Design Award tersebut, terdapat beberapa kategori award. Salah satunya adalah iPhone Game of the Year 2017 yang dimenangkan oleh game Splitter Critters.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_31727\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-31727\" data-attachment-id=\"31727\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iphone-game-of-the-year-2017/attachment/3-1-30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-1-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-1-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-1-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-31727\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-31727\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : developer.apple.com)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Game yang di-<em>design</em> untuk iPhone dan iPad ini adalah game yang dirancang dan dikembangkan oleh tim dari Vancouver, Kanada. Splitter Critters adalah permainan berbasis <em>puzzle arcade</em> untuk iPhone dan iPad dengan <em>mind bending</em> mekanika yang dapat dimainkan oleh semua umur.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_31724\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-31724\" data-attachment-id=\"31724\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iphone-game-of-the-year-2017/attachment/2-1-35/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-31724\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-31724\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : developer.apple.com)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dipilih sebagai pemenang Apple Design Award, karena game ini memiliki <em>touch-centric game play</em>, memiliki <em>absorbing sound design</em>, dan minimalis <em>paper-craft aestetic</em>. Permainan Splitter Critters menggunakan efek merobek dan teknik pengaturan ulang adegan untuk membantu pemain memecahkan teka-teki dengan cara baru. Dengan mekanika lingkungan yang cerdas seperti sinar laser, permukaan reflektif, cairan, platform bergerak, dan <em>soundscapes</em> yang mendalam untuk setiap dunia, aplikasi ini menawarkan pengalaman bermain yang inventif dan mudah diingat.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_31733\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-31733\" data-attachment-id=\"31733\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iphone-game-of-the-year-2017/attachment/5-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-31733\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/#splitter-critters)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-31733\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : developer.apple.com)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biar lebih asik memainkan game ini, bro sis bisa pake <em>headphone</em> atau <em>earphone</em> untuk mendengarkan efek-efek suara yang ada pada game ini, dan atur volumenya biar mainnya jadi lebih seru. Splitter Critters dirilis pertama kali di iOS, memanfaatkan iCloud dan Game Center, dan diterjemahkan ke dalam 15 bahasa.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_31730\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-31730\" data-attachment-id=\"31730\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/iphone-game-of-the-year-2017/attachment/4-1-30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-1-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/splitter-critters/)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/splitter-critters/)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-1-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-1-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-31730\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/splitter-critters/)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-31730\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber : itunes.apple.com)</p></div>\n<p>Berikut adalah detail tentang game Splitter Critters.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Category           :Games</li>\n<li>Updated            :Nov 09, 2017</li>\n<li>Version             :3</li>\n<li>Size                     :135 MB</li>\n<li>Languages       :English, Danish, Dutch, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Norwegian                                Bokmål, Portuguese, Russian, Simplified Chinese, Spanish, Swedish</li>\n<li>Seller                 :RAC7 Games</li>\n<li>© 2016 RAC7 Games</li>\n<li>Rated 4+</li>\n</ul>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"16cb0136-1e1c-5b02-882b-09ae6a24f12b"}}}